assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T06:20:16.000Z","msg":"台灣多數冇咁暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"760f45d28d6bac37086c3b2435ab8b1dbffe00be","tid":2507304,"uid":396048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T06:27:59.000Z","msg":"目前看起來色叔叔的下體是「回不去了」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db187c99623b7f5b7b4c8a4c71e52a400952ddb8","tid":2507304,"uid":274055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ace29fa1dbcb72ee4165b0f96ec830e9684aabf2","tid":2507304,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T02:21:17.000Z","msg":"巴西奧柳斯達瓜(Olhos D&rsquo;Agua)近日發生一起社會案件，一名年約20歲的女生，遭到36歲親叔叔調戲，甚至要霸王硬上弓。女生的男友後來得知後，撂人對叔叔採取報復行動，最後更斬斷叔叔的生殖器，並把「斷雞」直接拿去餵豬，讓叔叔剩下餘生成為名符其實的太監。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《每日星報》報導，據悉這名36歲男子日前酒醉後，調戲自己的親姪女，更試圖性侵，讓姪女相當害怕。姪女後來自行掙脫逃出，並把事件告訴給20歲男友，男友聽完後相當氣憤，但他不願意報警，而是決定動用私刑。本月19日，男友帶著自己的表親直接和男子面對面，男友將這位色叔叔引誘到甘蔗田之後，就和表親一起把色叔叔打爆，並打至昏迷，隨後更直接對他處以「宮刑」，當下斬斷他的生殖器，隨後將叔叔丟入灌木叢中，自己則取走被斬斷的陰莖與睪丸。<br />\n<br />\n色叔叔之後自己醒來，但是發現自己下半身不斷流血，痛不欲生，之後向附近民眾求助並被送往醫院急救。警官席爾瓦(Michael Stephan da Silva)表示，警方之後尋找被斬斷的肢體，無奈卻無任何發現，並相信可能已經被動物吃了。而目前最有可能吃掉色叔叔生殖器的動物，就是豬。<br />\n<br />\n負責治療色叔叔的醫師羅寶(Felipe Lobo)表示，色叔叔的下體受傷嚴重，醫師們透過手術，力保重建色叔叔的尿道，減輕他的痛苦，現在他的泌尿系統已逐漸恢復正常，大約住院2~4天就能回家休養。但羅寶也指出，目前看起來色叔叔的下體是「回不去了」，恐怕接下來的餘生都要過著太監生活。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210428/XE5LD34FV5H4JJ5IX5O3VJAPKY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210428%2FXE5LD34FV5H4JJ5IX5O3VJAPKY%2F&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0pugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=ac03e16e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210428%2FXE5LD34FV5H4JJ5IX5O3VJAPKY%2F&h=a9f1eeba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210428/XE5LD34FV5H4JJ5IX5O3VJAPKY/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T06:30:10.000Z","msg":"男友跟住就自己搞個女生"},{"pid":"5456f90e5821ab3cb5edbd55b354fbd0a75418a4","tid":2507304,"uid":52429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7daf613d0c4a358b3ef260b20e1111147337cbdf","tid":2507304,"uid":133806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b6a268ff84bf4e0aaaaf85137cc21caf2b17896","tid":2507304,"uid":52429,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T02:33:33.000Z","msg":"公公吖麼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Bq2MpXvgdKU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBq2MpXvgdKU&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0pugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=0c42d199\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Bq2MpXvgdKU</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T05:23:07.000Z","msg":"屌童年回憶嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T06:30:33.000Z","msg":"大家咁話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5857b06c1dd81bd40f67f9fa5fb8f35cfcda2f34","tid":2507304,"uid":62318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3054041e74f7e5917251967e081660944f900bc","tid":2507304,"uid":64981,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"c1725423ecbd04445bda688f819da22ade892f7d","tid":2507304,"uid":83060,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:19:56.000Z","msg":"收皮啦<br />\n如果你地姪女係咁咪一樣想搞<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.xvideos.com/video62468467/20297327/0/asiatica_inocent_sexy_y_linda\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xvideos.com%2Fvideo62468467%2F20297327%2F0%2Fasiatica_inocent_sexy_y_linda&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0pugP